<scenario>
The agent A provided the following violation scenario:
The for-loop iterates from 0 up to and including VOLATILE_DISK_LOC_MAX. When i == VOLATILE_DISK_LOC_MAX the switch falls through to the default branch which only sets tmpdir = NULL and then the subsequent if (tmpdir != NULL && ...) test fails. That extra iteration performs no meaningful action; removing the final iteration (changing <= to < or removing the default assignment) would not change the observable behavior of the function, so this is executed dead code.
</scenario>
